Discovery initial set of splits based on StreamingStartingStrategy. ContinuousEnumerationResult#splits() should contain initial splits discovered from table scan for StreamingStartingStrategy#TABLE_SCAN_THEN_INCREMENTAL. For all other strategies, splits collection should be empty. ContinuousEnumerationResult#toPosition() points to the starting position for the next incremental split discovery with exclusive behavior. Meaning files committed by the snapshot from the position inContinuousEnumerationResult won't be included in the next incremental scan.
